data.description: PRICED TO SELL! Welcome to this captivating waterfront home, step outside to a covered rear patio that spans the length of the house, offering picturesque views of the bayou beneath the cooling shade of an elegant oak tree. This property is a boater's dream with a spacious dock, a custom-built boat house, and a convenient lift, all constructed in 2012. Inside, you'll find a welcoming and open floor plan highlighted by an oversized den complete with a cozy fireplace. The kitchen has been tastefully updated with granite counters. A wet bar and a full bath downstairs add to the convenience of this home. Upstairs, you'll discover four bedrooms with huge closets, three of which have direct access to the rear covered patio, providing you with captivating waterfront views. The master suite stands out with custom barn doors and charming shiplap details, adding a touch of elegance to your personal space. With a little TLC you can make this paradise!
